{
  "stem": "10181.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't-- I didn't really bother me very much, my birthday, at the time, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't think about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, the next day or the day after, I think it was the-- it must have been the medical officer of the unit, you know, came, and he looked.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess he was in shock, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he decided right away that he has to evacuate the train, get everybody off that train first of all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you want to take care of them, can't leave them on the train, you know, packed like sardines and-- and-- and-- no proper sanitation, and-- and-- and no nothing, you know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started to take us to this little town where there was some buildings where-- with apartments which had been abandoned by German officers who had fled because of the advance of the American army.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put it in there together with another family, OK, another Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or-- there was a lady with-- with her son, and I think her husband already was dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't even remember the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she of course was older, so she tried to sort of, you know, look after us, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wasn't [INAUDIBLE] she was very sick herself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at one time or another, you know, when we went out, one of the soldiers would approach me and said, where are you from, and-- in German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, from Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, I'll take you back tomorrow to Holland, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted to, you know-- to be nice to us, you know, all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
